title: Moroccanoil Curl Control Mousse, 5.1 oz
description: Curly and tightly spiraled hair needs control without the crunch. Moroccanoil curl control mousse's lightweight yet powerful formula is enriched with argan oil to tame, define and hold curls naturally for hours while sealing in moisture and keeping out frizz. Curls and ringlets are left looking soft, smooth and natural in any weather.
